supporting_documents.sop: My name is Samira Perez, and I am applying for financial aid to pursue my Bachelor of Arts in Economics at Crestwood University. Financial aid will allow me to cover tuition, books, technology, and childcare costs while continuing to work and raise my daughter. I am committed to completing my program successfully and contributing to my community.
